name: Buuunggeeeeeeeee!!1
description:
The story is short. The flood was severe, the Wake island (western Pacific Ocean) is under the water. But the jumper (you) is already up, alone, and eager to experience. What is left? Where to go? What to eat? Whom to love? Why to not jump?

Ready to go? 3 2 1 Buuunggeeeeeeeee!!1
